        </item>
        <item>
            <title>特朗普社交平台 Truth 将上市　收购 SPAC 公司借壳上市</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/truth-social-on-verge-of-stock-market-approval/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=truth-social-on-verge-of-stock-market-approval</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/truth-social-on-verge-of-stock-market-approval/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 12:00:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[TRUTH Social]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[特朗普]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1226007</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>为了对抗被认为偏向左派的大型社交平台，前美国总统特朗普就创办 Truth Social，最近更打算透过 SPAC 方式收购空壳公司上市集资。<br /><span id="more-1226007"></span></p><p>据报导指，Digital World Acquisition Corporation（简称 DWAC）的股东近日批准与由特朗普主导的社交平台 Truth Social 合并。合并现在已经完成，将于纳斯达克以 DJT 代号上市，有估计指出特朗普的净资产将因此增加约 30 亿美元。</p><p>合并完成后，DWAC 的投资者将成为 Truth Social 母公司 Trump Media &amp; Technology Group（简称 TMTG）的股东。不过虽然合并成功后预计下星期就可以开始交易，TMTG 的发展仍然充满不确定性。合并宣布之后，DWAC 的股价最多曾下跌 12%。反映市场对 Truth Social 财务状况的担忧，始终这个平台自 2022 年成立以来一直都是蚀本状态，在 2023 年前九个月就报告了 4,900 万美元赤字，未来如何发展下去也仍然充满变数。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.foxbusiness.com/markets/truth-social-verge-stock-market-approval-potentially-netting-trump-billions">Fox</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/08/donald-trump-2/software/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">特朗普：上台后封杀 TikTok 与中国电动车　及向欧盟实施惩罚性贸易措施</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/truth-social-on-verge-of-stock-market-approval/life-tech/social-network/">特朗普社交平台 Truth 将上市　收购 SPAC 公司借壳上市</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/truth-social-on-verge-of-stock-market-approval/life-tech/social-network/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>微软新 Surface 大幅提升可维修性，零件刊载 QR Code、清晰标示螺丝种类与位置</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/%e5%be%ae%e8%bb%9f%e6%96%b0-surface-%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e5%8f%af%e7%b6%ad%e4%bf%ae%e6%80%a7-%e9%9b%b6%e4%bb%b6%e5%88%8a%e8%bc%89-qr-code%e3%80%81%e6%b8%85%e6%99%b0%e6%a8%99/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e5%25be%25ae%25e8%25bb%259f%25e6%2596%25b0-surface-%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25b9%2585%25e6%258f%2590%25e5%258d%2587%25e5%258f%25af%25e7%25b6%25ad%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e6%2580%25a7-%25e9%259b%25b6%25e4%25bb%25b6%25e5%2588%258a%25e8%25bc%2589-qr-code%25e3%2580%2581%25e6%25b8%2585%25e6%2599%25b0%25e6%25a8%2599</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/%e5%be%ae%e8%bb%9f%e6%96%b0-surface-%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e5%8f%af%e7%b6%ad%e4%bf%ae%e6%80%a7-%e9%9b%b6%e4%bb%b6%e5%88%8a%e8%bc%89-qr-code%e3%80%81%e6%b8%85%e6%99%b0%e6%a8%99/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 10:00:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1226057</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日 Microsoft 发布针对企业市场的全新 Surface Pro 10 和 Surface Laptop 6。这两款装置的卖点在于大大提升了维修便利性。两款手提电脑引入了一项创新维修方式：内部零件上贴有 QR 码，令超过十种关键零件的识别、更换都变得更容易。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1226062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/00_m-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/00_m-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/00_m-1.jpg 1120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1226063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/01-22-666x580.jpg" alt="" width="666" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/01-22-666x580.jpg 666w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/01-22.jpg 1033w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 666px" /></p><p>在 Surface Pro 10 中，用户能够轻松更换的部件包括显示屏模组、可拆卸的 SSD、电池、包含处理器和 RAM 的主机板、Surface Connect 端口、散热模组、咪高风模组、SSD 盖子、扬声器、外壳、前置和后置摄像头、电源按钮和音量按钮以及支架。而 Surface Laptop 6 也不例外，支援更换的零件包括显示屏组件、键盘、SSD、电池、主板、Surface Connect 端子、散热模组、音频插孔、扬声器、触控板和支架等。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1226060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/glbfuw-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/glbfuw-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/glbfuw.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>机身内部设计有大量提示让修理变得更方便，例如螺丝标签，每个零件显示使用哪种螺丝批，还有螺丝的数量。另一方面每个可更换零件都刊载有 QR 码，用户可打开更换该零件的说明书。</p><p>Microsoft 更与知名电子产品维修资讯网站 iFixit 合作推出专用修理工具。厂商积极提升产品可维修性，可减少废弃物和鼓励产品再利用。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/21/24107592/microsoft-surface-pro-10-laptop-6-repairability-servicing-qr-codes-screw-features">The Verge</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/%e5%be%ae%e8%bb%9f%e6%96%b0-surface-%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e5%8f%af%e7%b6%ad%e4%bf%ae%e6%80%a7-%e9%9b%b6%e4%bb%b6%e5%88%8a%e8%bc%89-qr-code%e3%80%81%e6%b8%85%e6%99%b0%e6%a8%99/fun-tech/">微软新 Surface 大幅提升可维修性，零件刊载 QR Code、清晰标示螺丝种类与位置</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
